org.bytedeco.bullet.LinearMath

Class btDefaultSerializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
      • org.bytedeco.bullet.LinearMath.btSerializer
        • org.bytedeco.bullet.LinearMath.btDefaultSerializer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    @NoOffset
 @Properties(inherit=LinearMath.class)
public class btDefaultSerializer
extends btSerializer
    The btDefaultSerializer is the main Bullet serialization class. The constructor takes an optional argument for backwards compatibility, it is recommended to leave this empty/zero.
